TitleEnglish: There Is Also a Hole in the Student Organization!
SummaryEnglish: The story is set at a prestigious school on the outskirts of town, where high school student Ume Mizunoe becomes a student council officer to avoid repeating a year. But the other members of the student council are silly, sulky, scary, and strangely cute. A strange and friendly high school life with unique student council members begin.
SummaryJapanese: 私立藤成学園高等部１年の水之江梅は国語の成績は抜群な一方、理系科目は進級に響くほど壊滅的。内申点をあげるため生徒会の役員となるもののそこにはカリスマむっつり、怖くて優しい清楚な会計、生意気可愛い男の子、小っちゃな捨て猫庶務など、何やら変わった子たちが勢揃いでドタバタな毎日が待ち受けていた！
Aliases: Seitokai ni mo Ana wa Aru!
